21 (11) A member of the Board who is appointed under paragraph (3)(iii)
22 through (vi) of this subsection may serve only two consecutive full 4–year terms, plus any
23 partial term served before the initial 4–year term.
24 (12) Subject to paragraphs (13) and (14) of this subsection, the Board shall
